---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use | Food Additive Regulation Database"
  description="Terms of use for the Food Additive Regulation Database."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-brand-50 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-white border-b border-brand-100 mb-12">
      <div class="container py-16 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
          Terms of <span class="text-accent">Use</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
          Last updated: April 3, 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container max-w-4xl space-y-12">
      <section class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-brand-100 prose prose-brand max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Acceptance of Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600 leading-relaxed">
          By accessing and using <span class="font-bold text-brand-900">food.matrix-db.com</span> (the "Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Nature of Information
        </h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-800">Informational Purpose Only</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          The Food Additive Regulation Database provides factual regulatory information compiled from official government sources. <span class="font-bold text-brand-900">This information is for informational purposes only and does NOT constitute:</span>
        </p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-brand-600 font-medium">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600">✕ Medical advice</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600">✕ Nutritional advice</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600">✕ Safety recommendations</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600">✕ Professional guidance</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-100 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2">Not a Substitute for Official Sources</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <span class="font-bold">Always verify information with official regulatory authorities.</span> Regulatory status can change, and you should refer to:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-bold text-brand-800">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> Your local food regulatory authority</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> Official government publications</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> Qualified professionals (dietitians, food scientists, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Accuracy and Completeness
        </h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-800">Best Efforts</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranties or representations about:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-600 font-medium">
          <li>• The accuracy or completeness of information on this site</li>
          <li>• The currentness of regulatory information</li>
          <li>• The suitability of information for any particular purpose</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mt-6">Information May Change</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          Food additive regulations change over time. Information on this site may become outdated. We are not responsible for keeping all information current in real-time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Disclaimer of Warranties
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-brand-500 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Legal Disclaimer</p>
          <p class="text-brand-800 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
            THE SITE AND ALL INFORMATION PROVIDED ARE ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS. WE MAKE NO WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO: WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, NON-INFRINGEMENT, OR ACCURACY OF INFORMATION.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, WE SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-600 font-medium">
          <li>• Direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
          <li>• Loss of profits or revenue</li>
          <li>• Health consequences arising from use of information</li>
          <li>• Damages resulting from reliance on information provided</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 text-red-700">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></span>
          Use at Your Own Risk
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-bold">
          You use this site and its information entirely at your own risk.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-600 mt-2">
          If you have health concerns, food allergies, or are making decisions that could affect health or safety, consult qualified professionals and official regulatory sources.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          External Links
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          Our site contains links to external websites (regulatory agencies, scientific publications, etc.). We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of external sites.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Intellectual Property
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          The compilation and presentation of data on this site is our intellectual property. The underlying regulatory data is public information from government sources.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Changes to Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600">
          These terms are governed by the laws of Japan. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Fukuoka, Japan.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-brand-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-16 -mt-16 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Contact & Operator
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 relative z-10">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 mb-2">Operator</div>
            <p class="text-brand-100 font-bold">SHOYA KIHARA</p>
            <div>
              <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 mb-2">Address</div>
              <p class="text-brand-100 font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">
                7F, Tenjin First Building, 4-6-28 Tenjin,<br/>
                Chuo-ku, Fukuoka-shi, Fukuoka 810-0001, Japan
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4">Questions?</div>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">contact@matrix-db.com</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-400 italic">For questions about these terms or our data practices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
